response.overview: On September 23rd GCW is back to the USA to presents Shooting Star live on FITE straight from the Ukrainian Cultural Center in Los Angeles, CA. The first matches in the lineup are already announced, check them below:  Tag Team Match  Joey Janela & Starboy Charlie vs The South Pacific Savages (Jacob Fatu & Juicy Finau)  Mance Warner vs Hunter Freeman  Arkangel Divino vs Ultimo Maldito  Jordan Oliver vs Kevin Blackwood  Jonathan Gresham vs Nick Wayne  GCW Tag Team Title Three Way Match  Mega Bastards (Alex Colon & John Wayne Murdoch) (c) vs Bussy (Allie Katch & Effy) vs Los Mazisos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)  GCW Extreme Title Match  Cole Radrick (c) vs Jack Cartwheel
response.title: GCW Shooting Star
